T1  - Does the internet defy the law of gravity?
AU  - Blum, Bernardo S.
AU  - Goldfarb, Avi
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 70
IS  - 2
SP  - 384
EP  - 405
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/12/01/
